scleaner (0.32.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Add a gnome shortcut. scleaner is put under Application;System;
  * David Paleino helps me to fix debian folder ... thanks!
  * You can now add directories in scan, there are 2 rules to know :
  * 1) If a folder is added (for example /home/snoogie/git/src) but his parent (for example /home/snoogie/) is already in the folder list, then scleaner won't add it with a wxMessageDialog for user notification.
  * 2) If a parent folder is added (for example /home/snoogie/) but some childs (for example /home/snoogie/git/, /home/snoogie/git2 or /home/snoogie/git/src) are already in the folder list, then scleaner will remove them from folders list.
  * Add CRC32 calc method in CEngine.
  * Add accelerators
  * scleaner now use git (bye bye subversion).
  * Moving all non GUI code from maininterface to engine.
  * Adding namespace to source code.
  * Adding menu icons.
  * New set of icons.
  * Add a null file size plugin.
  * Add an empty folder plugin.
  * Plugins can now pre-select founded files.

 -- Jean-Michel Frouin <jmfrouin@gmail.com>  Fri, 30 Sep 2007 23:44:26 +0200

